Amy Alistair Re Mosquitoes From zaeza Re Mosquitoes From Ed Gonzales Message Date Wed Oct From Amy Alistair Subject Mosquitoes I hate to do this and do not want to put anyone out but I need some help The mosquitoes are terrible It is hurting me to look at Kendall my son any more as the number of bites on him have gone into the double digits I cannot imagine that we are the only ones suffering from these nasty little pests and I want to do something about it If any of you have time tomorrow can you do me this can you call Harris County Mosquito Control and help me complain I figure that if a whole load of us start calling they wont be able to ignore us Their number is I get a recording when I call but their hours are so maybe we can talk to a live person tomorrow Thank you for helping me
